init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The people of Earth are highly protective and overbearing when it comes to their love for Matt Damon.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This may be the start of an intergalactic war.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They have decided to make a few concessions and allow the rescue mission to go forward.
